Add RUBYGEM_MIRROR parameter and fix required parameters issue

Add RUBYGEM_MIRROR parameter and fix required parameters issue

The new RUBYGEM_MIRROR parameter is added to allow custom RubyGems
mirror URL to be used if needed.

The required parameters need to be marked as required (*) to avoid
failure during the build process due to missing required parameters.

Signed-off-by: Vu Dinh <vdinh@redhat.com>
